23
00:01:49,171 --> 00:01:52,007

24
00:01:53,160 --> 00:01:55,860
Everyone, Master asked me to run an errand in Jin City.

25
00:01:55,860 --> 00:01:58,420
I'm afraid I can't go to the Tang Sect.

26
00:01:58,420 --> 00:02:00,100
I'll wait outside.

27
00:02:00,100 --> 00:02:04,660
Given your master's past grievances with them, it's best that you stay outside.

28
00:02:04,660 --> 00:02:06,700
Senior Liu Yue had a feud with the Tang Sect?

29
00:02:06,700 --> 00:02:08,580
Tell us about it.

30
00:02:08,580 --> 00:02:10,220
Why?

31
00:02:10,220 --> 00:02:12,660
Are you eager to find out?

32
00:02:12,660 --> 00:02:17,420
It's basically the bygone days of romance.

33
00:02:20,080 --> 00:02:22,980
Forget it. I wouldn't want Senior Liu Yue's wrath.

34
00:02:22,980 --> 00:02:28,000
- Junior Niece, see you around. 
 - Take care.

35
00:02:28,000 --> 00:02:32,680
Why do you get all nervous when you find it's something romantic?

36
00:02:33,300 --> 00:02:35,300
Shut it.

37
00:02:46,300 --> 00:02:48,460
Stay safe!

38
00:02:56,725 --> 00:03:01,050

39
00:03:01,940 --> 00:03:03,820
The Tang Sect.

40
00:03:03,820 --> 00:03:07,860
This mansion is bigger than Marquis Zhenxi's Mansion.

41
00:03:09,780 --> 00:03:11,600
This is where we part ways.

42
00:03:11,600 --> 00:03:13,080
Take care.

43
00:03:13,880 --> 00:03:15,780
You're leaving already?

44
00:03:18,480 --> 00:03:20,340
Fine.

45
00:03:20,340 --> 00:03:24,280
Brother Yun, take care.

46
00:03:25,540 --> 00:03:27,120
Take care.

47
00:03:27,860 --> 00:03:29,620
Sir.

48
00:03:30,900 --> 00:03:32,600
Take care.

49
00:03:36,650 --> 00:03:39,910

50
00:03:56,600 --> 00:03:58,360
 Master!

51
00:03:59,380 --> 00:04:01,280
 - Oh no!  
 - Xiao Baili.

52
00:04:01,280 --> 00:04:03,340
In a hurry to go somewhere?

53
00:04:03,340 --> 00:04:05,520
Uncle. My friend was abducted into the Tang Sect.

54
00:04:05,520 --> 00:04:07,600
I must rescue him.

55
00:04:08,260 --> 00:04:11,300
Who are you? Tell me your names.

56
00:04:13,640 --> 00:04:15,520
Wen Hujiu of the Wen Family.

57
00:04:15,520 --> 00:04:17,260
Baili Dongjun.

58
00:04:17,260 --> 00:04:19,600
- Invitation? 
 - I don't have one.

59
00:04:19,600 --> 00:04:23,120
It's with my friend. He was dragged into your mansion.

60
00:04:23,120 --> 00:04:26,640
- Absurd. 
 - That's the truth. Stop wasting my time.

61
00:04:26,640 --> 00:04:29,000
- I must find him. 
 - Trespassers must be killed!

62
00:04:29,000 --> 00:04:32,200
 Trespassers must be killed!

63
00:04:33,120 --> 00:04:34,640
You have two options.

64
00:04:34,640 --> 00:04:36,680
One, let me in.

65
00:04:36,680 --> 00:04:41,500
Two, meet my blade and let me in.

66
00:04:41,500 --> 00:04:43,360
What a fool.

67
00:04:51,260 --> 00:04:54,100
 His fist is actually as hard as the sword.

68
00:05:00,180 --> 00:05:01,960
I don't want to fight a nobody.

69
00:05:01,960 --> 00:05:03,640
Tell me your name.

70
00:05:03,640 --> 00:05:05,640
I am Tang Lianyue of the Tang Sect.

71
00:05:05,640 --> 00:05:09,260
I am Baili Dongjun of the Jixia Academy.

72
00:05:14,080 --> 00:05:15,640
There's no need for a fight.

73
00:05:15,640 --> 00:05:18,640
And you! That was uncalled for.

74
00:05:20,000 --> 00:05:22,840
Mr. Wen. Trespassers must be killed.

75
00:05:22,840 --> 00:05:24,520
That's the rule here.

76
00:05:24,520 --> 00:05:25,980
I have the invitation.

77
00:05:25,980 --> 00:05:29,600
He is my nephew. How is he a trespasser?

78
00:05:31,280 --> 00:05:34,680
In that case, follow me and rest at the side chamber.

79
00:05:34,680 --> 00:05:36,420
Wait.

80
00:05:36,420 --> 00:05:40,080
Whoever abducted my friend could be from your sect.

81
00:05:40,080 --> 00:05:41,780
You want me to rest?

82
00:05:41,780 --> 00:05:43,580
I wonder why.

83
00:05:43,580 --> 00:05:46,620
A member of our sect would never stoop that low.

84
00:05:46,620 --> 00:05:48,400
Your friend was trespassing.

85
00:05:48,400 --> 00:05:51,640
I will find him and kill him.

86
00:05:51,640 --> 00:05:53,520
I dare you.

87
00:05:54,780 --> 00:05:58,040
Lianyue is Grandmaster Tang's last disciple in the Tang Sect.

88
00:05:58,040 --> 00:06:00,620
You are the last disciple of Mister Li from the Academy.

89
00:06:00,620 --> 00:06:04,800
Mister Li and Grandmaster Tang have the same seniority.

90
00:06:05,480 --> 00:06:07,760
You might as well be friends.

91
00:06:07,760 --> 00:06:11,340
Shake hands and put all of this behind us.

92
00:06:12,660 --> 00:06:14,500
- If he's a member of the Tang Sect... 
 - Even if it's Mister Li, so what?

93
00:06:14,500 --> 00:06:16,700
- there's no need for me to do that. 
 - Not interested.

94
00:06:16,700 --> 00:06:19,400
Forget it. Young people like you know nothing.

95
00:06:19,400 --> 00:06:24,320
Lianyue, I'll need you to arrange accommodation for us.

96
00:06:27,460 --> 00:06:29,260
You...

97
00:06:31,740 --> 00:06:33,680
Uncle. What about my friend?

98
00:06:33,680 --> 00:06:35,840
The Poison Convention is tomorrow.

99
00:06:35,840 --> 00:06:41,130
Given the timing of his abduction, it must be linked to the convention.

100
00:06:41,130 --> 00:06:43,110
Let's head inside.

101
00:06:43,110 --> 00:06:45,270

102
00:06:53,200 --> 00:06:56,840
The Poison Convention will be held tomorrow at noon.

103
00:06:56,840 --> 00:07:00,480
If we find your friend, I'll send someone to inform you.

104
00:07:00,480 --> 00:07:04,900
Remember, do not wander around.

105
00:07:13,480 --> 00:07:15,820
This is a nice room.

106
00:07:18,120 --> 00:07:21,200
Uncle. We have to rescue my friend.

107
00:07:21,200 --> 00:07:25,000
I was going to ask you. Weren't you with Mister Li?

108
00:07:25,000 --> 00:07:26,890
Where did he go?

109
00:07:26,890 --> 00:07:30,060
And who is the one who got abducted?

110
00:07:31,080 --> 00:07:37,830
The person who got abducted was my master's friend.

111
00:07:37,830 --> 00:07:42,960
I was going to meet up with my master after the Poison Convention.

112
00:07:42,960 --> 00:07:45,120
What about his prowess?

113
00:07:45,980 --> 00:07:52,520
As of now, it's about my level.

114
00:07:52,520 --> 00:07:57,580
That means whoever abducted your friend was not ordinary.

115
00:07:57,580 --> 00:07:59,000
Don't worry.

116
00:07:59,000 --> 00:08:01,780
No one would dare kill anyone so blatantly in the Tang Sect.

117
00:08:01,780 --> 00:08:04,080
Your friend must have been hidden.

118
00:08:04,080 --> 00:08:08,080
Perhaps we'll learn the truth tomorrow during the Poison Convention.

119
00:08:08,080 --> 00:08:11,780
But this friend of mine means a lot to me.

120
00:08:13,260 --> 00:08:14,800
Uncle...

121
00:08:22,380 --> 00:08:27,440
 I handed over my master's token to Riverside Manor's base in Jin City.

122
00:08:27,440 --> 00:08:30,680
 I wonder how Martial Uncle Baili and the rest are doing right now.

123
00:08:30,680 --> 00:08:32,560
 There's not much else to do.

124
00:08:32,560 --> 00:08:34,300
 I should go and meet her.

125
00:08:34,300 --> 00:08:36,760

126
00:08:36,760 --> 00:08:38,800
Come on!

127
00:08:39,380 --> 00:08:41,040
Follow my bet!

128
00:08:41,040 --> 00:08:43,540
You'll win for sure! Follow me, you'll win!

129
00:08:43,540 --> 00:08:46,720
Don't you have faith in me? How can you not trust me?

130
00:08:46,720 --> 00:08:49,720
- Just do as I do. 
 - Everybody!

131
00:08:49,720 --> 00:08:52,140
Have you placed your bet?

132
00:08:52,140 --> 00:08:55,780
Miss, if I'm not mistaken,

133
00:08:55,780 --> 00:08:58,880
I own this gambling parlor.

134
00:08:58,880 --> 00:09:01,920
How are you calling the shots now?

135
00:09:04,260 --> 00:09:06,040
My apologies, Boss Mu.

136
00:09:06,040 --> 00:09:08,520
I'm used to it.

137
00:09:08,520 --> 00:09:11,000
Have you placed your bet?

138
00:09:14,420 --> 00:09:17,760
Miss, we'll see if you can still win.

139
00:09:17,760 --> 00:09:22,140
Boss Mu, haven't you heard?

140
00:09:22,140 --> 00:09:24,240
We're the masters of our destiny.

141
00:09:24,240 --> 00:09:28,140
- Certainly. What about it? 
 - Nothing.

142
00:09:28,140 --> 00:09:32,540
I just want you to know that the saying is nothing but a lie.

143
00:09:32,540 --> 00:09:33,900
Destiny is destiny.

144
00:09:33,900 --> 00:09:38,320
When it comes crashing down, we are all doomed.

145
00:09:38,320 --> 00:09:40,400
What's the tile?

146
00:09:40,400 --> 00:09:42,300
Double Heaven!

147
00:09:42,900 --> 00:09:45,260
Thank you!

148
00:09:49,000 --> 00:09:56,400
She said that because you were going to lose your entire gambling parlor to her.

149
00:10:01,100 --> 00:10:03,200
Sister Yue Yao?

150
00:10:03,200 --> 00:10:04,900
Sister Luoxia.

151
00:10:05,600 --> 00:10:10,200
Boss Mu. That's all for today.

152
00:10:10,200 --> 00:10:12,100
Record all this carefully.

153
00:10:12,100 --> 00:10:13,600
We'll have a rematch another day.

154
00:10:13,600 --> 00:10:15,000
Have fun everyone.

155
00:10:15,000 --> 00:10:17,500
- Let's go. 
 - I'm done with this.

156
00:10:17,500 --> 00:10:18,800
- Forget it. 
 - Let's go.

157
00:10:18,800 --> 00:10:20,300
Time to go home.

158
00:10:20,300 --> 00:10:23,700

159
00:10:28,200 --> 00:10:31,300
I'm here to run some errands for my master.

160
00:10:31,300 --> 00:10:36,700
As soon as I arrived, I heard rumors of a mysterious woman winning big in the gambling parlor.

161
00:10:36,700 --> 00:10:39,800
I knew it was you. So I came right away.

162
00:10:39,800 --> 00:10:41,600
Master?

163
00:10:42,500 --> 00:10:47,300
The most gorgeous man alive you mentioned in the letter?

164
00:10:47,300 --> 00:10:48,600
Correct.

165
00:10:48,600 --> 00:10:51,500
I took on your identity to become his disciple.

166
00:10:51,500 --> 00:10:56,200
If it's possible, I hope you can become his disciple too.

167
00:10:57,180 --> 00:11:01,300
The peerlessly handsome Young Master Liu Yue.

168
00:11:01,300 --> 00:11:04,700
Interesting. I should meet him.

169
00:11:04,700 --> 00:11:08,400
We'll see if he is more charming than you.

170
00:11:08,400 --> 00:11:10,200
Sister.

171
00:11:10,200 --> 00:11:12,600
I'm done teasing you. Come on.

172
00:11:12,600 --> 00:11:18,700
I want to hear all about the interesting things you encountered in Tianqi City.

173
00:11:20,500 --> 00:11:21,500

174
00:11:21,500 --> 00:11:22,700
- The invitation? 
 - Here you are.

175
00:11:22,700 --> 00:11:23,900
- Fine. Come in. 
 - Come in.

176
00:11:23,900 --> 00:11:25,300
Senior, let's go.

177
00:11:25,300 --> 00:11:26,700
- Invitation? 
 - Let's go.

178
00:11:26,700 --> 00:11:28,000
- This way. 
 - Sure.

179
00:11:28,000 --> 00:11:29,490
Invitation?

180
00:11:29,490 --> 00:11:31,200
Let's sit together.

181
00:11:31,200 --> 00:11:34,900
Had I not come here, you'd run out of medicine.

182
00:11:34,900 --> 00:11:39,000
You'd die here. Aren't you worried?

183
00:11:39,000 --> 00:11:40,500
Does it matter?

184
00:11:40,500 --> 00:11:44,600
Dying in the Martial World is better than dying in Medicine Valley.

185
00:11:44,600 --> 00:11:48,500
Your trip to Tianqi City didn't break your spirit.

186
00:11:49,180 --> 00:11:52,260
Stop standing there. Let's go.

187
00:11:56,260 --> 00:11:59,440
You've been through a lot.

188
00:12:01,340 --> 00:12:05,060
However, I have a question.

189
00:12:05,060 --> 00:12:07,620
What is it you want to know?

190
00:12:08,940 --> 00:12:18,060
Your identity, your goal, and the cold power struggle aside,

191
00:12:19,300 --> 00:12:24,100
are you in love with Baili Dongjun?

192
00:12:24,540 --> 00:12:25,980
I...

193
00:12:33,100 --> 00:12:36,600

194
00:12:38,820 --> 00:12:43,700
If we can't find your friend today, I'll talk to Grandmaster Tang for you.

195
00:12:43,700 --> 00:12:45,520
Thank you, Uncle.

196
00:12:46,220 --> 00:12:49,620
- What's over there? 
 - The Poison Convention.

197
00:12:50,600 --> 00:12:52,400
That's the Poison Convention?

198
00:12:52,400 --> 00:12:54,100
Won't you go there?

199
00:12:55,500 --> 00:12:59,000
The Convention over here is meant for the normal poison sects.

200
00:12:59,000 --> 00:13:02,000
It seems lively, but it has very little content in it.

201
00:13:02,000 --> 00:13:06,800
The real Poison Convention is always held in Grandmaster Tang's Wutong Yard.

202
00:13:06,800 --> 00:13:10,900
Only the five major poison sects are participating.

203
00:13:10,900 --> 00:13:12,400
That's a small circle.

204
00:13:12,400 --> 00:13:13,800
That's only a Poison Gathering.

205
00:13:13,800 --> 00:13:16,800
Yes. It's only a gathering.

206
00:13:16,800 --> 00:13:18,700
This way please.

207
00:13:18,700 --> 00:13:20,300
Let's go.

208
00:13:26,830 --> 00:13:28,990

209
00:13:33,400 --> 00:13:36,300
The man in black on the stage is Tang Linghuang.

210
00:13:36,300 --> 00:13:38,300
He is the Tang Sect's spokesperson.

211
00:13:38,300 --> 00:13:40,400
It's said he has the best poison.

212
00:13:40,400 --> 00:13:42,400
and hidden weapon user in the sect.

213
00:13:42,400 --> 00:13:46,800
This time I came here to test my skills against his.

214
00:13:47,700 --> 00:13:50,800
As for the rest, they are the elites of the five poison sects.

215
00:13:50,800 --> 00:13:52,600
This is the Poison God Sect.

216
00:13:52,600 --> 00:13:54,300
That is the Withered Cloud Sect.

217
00:13:54,300 --> 00:13:56,500
And the Undying Sect...

218
00:13:59,500 --> 00:14:01,200
What is Xiao Liu's sister doing here?

219
00:14:01,200 --> 00:14:04,200
- I miscalculated. 
 - Who are the others?

220
00:14:04,200 --> 00:14:06,600
The Five-Poison Clan.

221
00:14:06,600 --> 00:14:09,000
The poison using sects are truly menacing.

222
00:14:09,000 --> 00:14:11,200
Their names carry either death or poison.

223
00:14:11,200 --> 00:14:15,200
- It seems they want the world to know they are nasty. 
 - Certainly.

224
00:14:15,200 --> 00:14:17,500
We're the nice people here. We are friendly.

225
00:14:17,500 --> 00:14:21,300
The Wen Family is all about grace and elegance.

226
00:14:21,300 --> 00:14:25,300
All right, enough about them. In any case they aren't as amazing as me.

227
00:14:27,180 --> 00:14:29,980
- Xiao Baili! 
 - Uncle Buping.

228
00:14:29,980 --> 00:14:31,620
What timing!

229
00:14:31,620 --> 00:14:34,020
Just in time.

230
00:14:43,100 --> 00:14:45,600
You're not a poison user. What are you doing here?

231
00:14:45,600 --> 00:14:47,000
Medicine and poison are related.

232
00:14:47,000 --> 00:14:49,600
I don't use poisons, but I know about them.

233
00:14:49,600 --> 00:14:51,800
If you can't stand that, stop wasting your time here.

234
00:14:51,800 --> 00:14:55,000
- I'm done talking to you. 
 - You lost the argument.

235
00:14:57,860 --> 00:15:00,700
King of Medicine, wait for me.

236
00:15:00,700 --> 00:15:02,300
Changfeng?

237
00:15:03,700 --> 00:15:06,200
Dongjun? What are you doing here?

238
00:15:06,200 --> 00:15:08,200
It's a long story.

239
00:15:08,200 --> 00:15:10,000
Everyone.

240
00:15:21,000 --> 00:15:24,000
As we all know, in the Martial World,

241
00:15:24,000 --> 00:15:27,800
the art of toxin is looked down upon as a form of Sly Path.

242
00:15:27,800 --> 00:15:30,300
It's not acknowledged by the world.

243
00:15:30,300 --> 00:15:33,800
The Tang Sect were shunned by the world for many years

244
00:15:33,800 --> 00:15:38,200
due to our expertise in poisons and hidden weapons.

245
00:15:38,200 --> 00:15:41,740
Today, when we mention the Tang Sect,

246
00:15:41,740 --> 00:15:47,300
is there anyone out there who would dare shun us?

247
00:15:48,300 --> 00:15:50,260
- Indeed. 
 - Indeed.

248
00:15:50,900 --> 00:15:52,100
- He is right. 
 - Yes.

249
00:15:52,100 --> 00:15:55,700
Sly Path or Right Path, it's nothing but prejudice.

250
00:15:55,700 --> 00:15:59,900
Poisons can take lives and save lives.

251
00:15:59,900 --> 00:16:04,200
Today, we shall attend this Poison Convention together.

252
00:16:04,200 --> 00:16:08,000
I hope that all of us can exchange knowledge to our heart's content

253
00:16:08,000 --> 00:16:10,800
and make the use of poison great again!

254
00:16:15,100 --> 00:16:19,800
It sounds like a sham we run into on the roads that is recruiting.

255
00:16:19,800 --> 00:16:23,800
- Right? Right? 
 - I didn't know that side of you, Mr. Wen.

256
00:16:23,800 --> 00:16:28,200
Uncle, I have a feeling you are jealous of him.

257
00:16:28,940 --> 00:16:32,280
The Wen Family never likes to show off.

258
00:16:32,280 --> 00:16:34,400
But your uncle wasn't born with that sense.

259
00:16:34,400 --> 00:16:36,300
He's always looking for a fight.

260
00:16:36,300 --> 00:16:39,700
The Tang Sect is hosting the Poison Convention

