Consider it his compensation for you.

509
00:38:52,060 --> 00:38:55,240
But why did he want to become mortal again?

510
00:38:57,160 --> 00:39:02,420
Lianyue, you are too young to understand it.

511
00:39:02,420 --> 00:39:05,720
With mortality, life is short.

512
00:39:05,720 --> 00:39:10,220
But if you were given 8000 years to live,

513
00:39:10,220 --> 00:39:14,880
would you be able to withstand the endless loneliness?

514
00:39:14,880 --> 00:39:20,320
You'd have to watch all of your loved ones pass away until there's no one left but you.

515
00:39:20,320 --> 00:39:22,280
Nonsense.

516
00:39:24,060 --> 00:39:25,700
Master.

517
00:39:25,700 --> 00:39:27,800
That felt nice.

518
00:39:36,100 --> 00:39:43,240
Allow me to introduce myself. I am Nangong Chunshui. I am a gentle scholar.

519
00:39:51,500 --> 00:39:53,100
Everyone.

520
00:39:54,200 --> 00:39:57,440
This is where I bid you farewell.

521
00:39:58,360 --> 00:40:02,100
I stirred up quite the commotion because of my personal goal.

522
00:40:02,100 --> 00:40:05,760
I hope you don't hold it against me,
Grandmaster Tang.

523
00:40:08,340 --> 00:40:12,340
My fellow disciples will be known across the world.

524
00:40:12,340 --> 00:40:16,940
As for you, you shall be their powerful rival.

525
00:40:16,940 --> 00:40:21,500
With you around, the Tang Sect shall stand strong.

526
00:40:23,260 --> 00:40:26,140
What? Are you a fortune-teller?

527
00:40:26,140 --> 00:40:30,420
Since you brought that up, I did work as one for a couple of years.

528
00:40:31,660 --> 00:40:34,840
You two brats, time to go.

529
00:40:34,840 --> 00:40:36,700
Two?

530
00:40:39,220 --> 00:40:40,900
Does that mean...

531
00:40:43,260 --> 00:40:45,660
Sikong Changfeng.

532
00:40:46,740 --> 00:40:49,640
- What is it? 
 - Nothing serious.

533
00:40:49,640 --> 00:40:55,020
I wonder if you're willing to be my disciple.

534
00:40:57,000 --> 00:41:00,020
What are you waiting for? Say yes.

535
00:41:06,900 --> 00:41:10,080
Rascal. Say yes.

536
00:41:10,080 --> 00:41:13,740
It's good to be his disciple.

537
00:41:13,740 --> 00:41:17,140
Our contract ends today.

538
00:41:17,140 --> 00:41:20,900
From now on I'm only half a master to you.

539
00:41:36,420 --> 00:41:38,100
Thank you, Master.

540
00:41:42,940 --> 00:41:45,540
Very well. I accept the offer.

541
00:41:45,540 --> 00:41:47,380
Kneel.

542
00:41:54,220 --> 00:41:57,740
Master, please accept my bow.

543
00:42:08,100 --> 00:42:09,820
Very well.

544
00:42:09,820 --> 00:42:14,360
From now on, you are a disciple of me, Nangong Chunshui.

545
00:42:17,340 --> 00:42:20,220
Get up, my junior.

546
00:42:21,060 --> 00:42:25,100
Baili Dongjun, strictly speaking, you are Mister Li's disciple.

547
00:42:25,100 --> 00:42:26,780
Don't take advantage of me.

548
00:42:26,780 --> 00:42:29,140
I don't care. You're my junior.

549
00:42:29,140 --> 00:42:31,020
Enough.

550
00:42:31,020 --> 00:42:34,260
You two, it's time to move on.

551
00:42:34,260 --> 00:42:36,580
Sure. I'll get the horses.

552
00:42:37,500 --> 00:42:40,360
I've waited for too long. I'm tired of it.

553
00:42:40,360 --> 00:42:42,640
We'll fly there.

554
00:42:42,640 --> 00:42:45,720
Grandmaster Tang, you know where we're heading.

555
00:42:45,720 --> 00:42:47,840
Please send the carriage there.

556
00:42:47,840 --> 00:42:49,760
I have a few jars of fine liquor in it.

557
00:42:49,760 --> 00:42:55,820
I wouldn't mind having a few jars of the Tang Sect's Drunken World.

558
00:42:57,220 --> 00:42:58,940
That settles it.

559
00:42:59,700 --> 00:43:01,140
Let's go.

560
00:43:01,140 --> 00:43:03,180
Wait, Master.

561
00:43:03,180 --> 00:43:05,540
My uncles, I'll take my leave.

562
00:43:05,540 --> 00:43:08,060
Send my regards to my family.

563
00:43:08,060 --> 00:43:10,360
I'm leaving. Take good care of yourself.

564
00:43:10,360 --> 00:43:13,620
- Don't worry about me. 
 - Enough chitchat. Let's go!

565
00:43:13,620 --> 00:43:17,220
Master! Don't forget Martial Niece!

566
00:43:19,260 --> 00:43:23,900
I have a hunch you have a perilous future ahead.

567
00:43:25,380 --> 00:43:27,380
Mind your own business.

568
00:43:30,800 --> 00:43:35,480

569
00:43:39,780 --> 00:43:43,100
My disciples, why do I feel nervous?

570
00:43:45,140 --> 00:43:46,540
This is it?

571
00:43:46,540 --> 00:43:49,860
Master, aren't we going to Xueyue City?

572
00:43:49,860 --> 00:43:53,900
But the sign says "Lower District".

573
00:43:54,980 --> 00:43:58,520
This city was once called Great Changhe.

574
00:43:58,520 --> 00:44:03,420
The first character of the name means "big", but it's a very small city.

575
00:44:03,420 --> 00:44:07,880
The place is remote with picturesque scenery. It's peaceful.

576
00:44:07,880 --> 00:44:11,760
Then, four peerless elites came to live in seclusion.

577
00:44:11,760 --> 00:44:15,500
And that somehow attracted more people to settle down here.

578
00:44:15,500 --> 00:44:18,040
So the city expanded.

579
00:44:18,040 --> 00:44:24,180
Later on, it was divided into two districts, named Upper District and Lower District.

580
00:44:24,180 --> 00:44:26,380
Wind for Lower District, blossoms for Upper District.

581
00:44:26,380 --> 00:44:28,700
Snow for the Cangshan mountain. Moon for the Erhai Lake.

582
00:44:28,700 --> 00:44:33,000
People then combined the names of both districts into Xueyue City.

583
00:44:33,000 --> 00:44:39,120
Out of the four elites I mentioned just now, only the Sword Deity had descendants.

584
00:44:39,120 --> 00:44:43,720
The people elected this descendant to become the city lord of Xueyue City.

585
00:44:43,720 --> 00:44:47,660
The current city lord is a woman.

586
00:44:47,660 --> 00:44:51,220
She loves dressing in red.

587
00:44:52,020 --> 00:44:54,760
There is a cinnabar mark between her brows.

588
00:44:54,760 --> 00:44:57,360
Her beauty is peerless.

589
00:44:58,060 --> 00:45:01,100
Her swordplay is invincible.

590
00:45:13,820 --> 00:45:15,960
She is the woman I love.

591
00:45:15,960 --> 00:45:18,080
I dream of her every day.

592
00:45:18,080 --> 00:45:21,200
I love her so much.

593
00:45:27,660 --> 00:45:30,620
Master, you must be truly nervous.

594
00:45:30,620 --> 00:45:33,820
- What? 
 - People get chatty when they are nervous.

595
00:45:33,820 --> 00:45:37,260
Master. You're almost 200 years old.

596
00:45:37,260 --> 00:45:40,480
- You're still bound by human emotions. 
 - Go away.

597
00:45:44,340 --> 00:45:46,260
Someone is coming this way.

598
00:45:54,620 --> 00:45:57,840
Calm down. She is one of us.

599
00:46:01,940 --> 00:46:04,120
Who are you?

600
00:46:06,820 --> 00:46:09,460
Long time no see, Miss Luo.

601
00:46:09,460 --> 00:46:11,440
Pardon the intrusion.

602
00:46:11,440 --> 00:46:14,780
I am Nangong Chunshui.

603
00:46:14,780 --> 00:46:18,760
I don't remember anyone by the name of Nangong Chunshui.

604
00:46:18,760 --> 00:46:22,790
That's because I had a different name

605
00:46:24,300 --> 00:46:26,260
when we first met.

606
00:46:26,260 --> 00:46:27,820
You...

607
00:46:33,380 --> 00:46:35,660
It really is you.

608
00:46:35,660 --> 00:46:37,660
Why are you here again?

609
00:46:38,300 --> 00:46:39,580
Master.

610
00:46:39,580 --> 00:46:41,700
She's the woman you're in love with?

611
00:46:41,700 --> 00:46:44,740
She doesn't seem to like you at all.

612
00:46:44,740 --> 00:46:46,780
Nonsense.

613
00:46:47,740 --> 00:46:52,300
Miss Luo and I are meant for each other.

614
00:46:52,300 --> 00:46:54,980
We made a vow of life when we first met.

615
00:46:55,740 --> 00:46:58,440
You're just a playboy and a heart breaker.

616
00:47:02,120 --> 00:47:06,220
Miss Luo, after so many years, you're still as ill-tempered.

617
00:47:06,220 --> 00:47:09,700
You're the greatest martial artist. I can't slay you.

